{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id77f32a9e-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s77vvv"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"77vvv"},"text":"§ 77vvv.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Judicial review","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id77f32a9f-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s77vvv/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Review of orders","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Orders of the Commission under this subchapter (including orders pursuant to the provisions of sections 77eee(b) and 77ggg(c) of this title) shall be subject to review in the same manner, upon the same conditions, and to the same extent, as provided in section 9 of the Securities Act of 1933 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s77i"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 77i","children":[],"tail":"], with respect to orders of the Commission under such Act."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id77f32aa0-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s77vvv/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Jurisdiction of offenses and suits","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Jurisdiction of offenses and violations under, and jurisdiction and venue of suits and actions brought to enforce any liability or duty created by, this subchapter, or any rules or regulations or orders prescribed under the authority thereof, shall be as provided in section 22(a) of the Securities Act of 1933 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s77v/a"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 77v(a)","children":[],"tail":"]."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id77f32aa1-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1933-05-27/ch38"},"text":"May 27, 1933, ch. 38","children":[],"tail":", title III, § 322, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1939-08-03/ch411"},"text":"Aug. 3, 1939, ch. 411","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/53/1175"},"text":"53 Stat. 1175","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/550/tIV/s418"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–550, title IV, § 418","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-11-15"},"text":"Nov. 15, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/2732"},"text":"104 Stat. 2732","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id77f32aa2-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id77f32aa3-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id77f32aa4-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Such Act, referred to in subsec. (a), means the Securities Act of 1933, approved ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1933-05-27/ch38"},"text":"May 27, 1933, ch. 38","children":[],"tail":", title I, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/74"},"text":"48 Stat. 74","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to subchapter I (§ 77a et seq.) of this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s77a"},"text":"section 77a of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id77f32aa5-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1990—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/550"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–550","children":[],"tail":" inserted “or duty” after “any liability”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"execDoc","id":"id77f32aa6-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Documents","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"transferOfFunctions","id":"id77f59ba7-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For transfer of functions of Securities and Exchange Commission, with certain exceptions, to Chairman of such Commission, see Reorg. Plan No. 10 of 1950, §§ 1, 2, eff. ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1950-05-24"},"text":"May 24, 1950","children":[],"tail":", 15 F.R. 3175, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/1265"},"text":"64 Stat. 1265","children":[],"tail":", set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s78d"},"text":"section 78d of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
